long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Can you beat AI?
"X & O" is a classic Tic-Tac-Toe game brought to your Chrome browser. Play against an AI opponent, aiming for victory with 'O' on a 3x3 grid. Track wins, losses, and ties, and toggle themes for a personalized touch. Enjoy timeless fun and strategic challenges, all in one Chrome extension.
